('list object',6,'Syntax: .list object #gameobject_id [#max_count]\r\n\r\nOutput gameobjects with gameobject id #gameobject_id found in world. Output gameobject guids and coordinates sorted by distance from character. Will be output maximum #max_count gameobject. If #max_count not provided use 10 as default value.'),
